  "prompt": "1970s surreal dark fantasy painting, style of Zdzisław Beksiński. An ancient library where the bookshelves are massive, calcified ribcages. The books are bound in pulsing, fleshy membranes, their titles glowing faintly like bruised veins. A solitary scholar, whose eyes have been replaced by a single, large, glowing amber gemstone, reads a scroll that seems to bleed black ink onto the floor. Sickly, dim lighting, claustrophobic atmosphere, intellectual madness. Palette of dried blood red, pale yellow parchment, and bruised purple. Gritty analog texture, masterful shading, no text, no canvas edges. --ar 9:16",
